          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "SecurityEvent\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| where EventID in (4624, 4625)\n| where LogonType == 10\n| extend SrcIP = iff(isempty(IpAddress) or IpAddress == '-', 'local/unknown', IpAddress)\n| summarize Attempts = count(), Failed = countif(EventID == 4625), Success = countif(EventID == 4624), TargetsAttempted = dcount(TargetUserName), Targets = make_set(TargetUserName, 8), Hosts = dcount(Computer), HostList = make_set(Computer, 6), Workstations = make_set(WorkstationName, 6), FirstSeen = min(TimeGenerated), LastSeen = max(TimeGenerated) by SrcIP\n| extend FailRate = round(100.0 * Failed / Attempts, 1)\n| project SrcIP, Attempts, Failed, Success, FailRate, TargetsAttempted, Targets, Hosts, HostList, Workstations, FirstSeen, LastSeen\n| top 25 by Attempts desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "RDP / Port 3389 Logon Abuse (4624 & 4625 Type 10) Brute Force & Lateral Movement",
