              "query": "MicrosoftGraphActivityLogs\n| where TimeGenerated {TimeRange}\n| summarize Calls = count(), Errors = countif(ResponseStatusCode >= 400), Apps = dcount(AppId), LastSeen = max(TimeGenerated) by SourceIP = tostring(IPAddress)\n| top 25 by Calls desc",
